## 🚀 Getting Started

Since this is a client-side web application, installation is immediate.

1.  Clone or download the repository to your local machine.
2.  Open the folder containing the project files.
3.  Double-click `index.html` to run it in any modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge).

